{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \u8220"Hello, this is the Earth Security Agency.\u8221" The receptionist said. \u8220"How can I help you?\u8221" She listened over the phone to Aria for a few moments, jotting down details on a notepad. \u8220"Alright ma\u8217'am, I understand. Just stay calm and we\u8217'll send someone round to deal with it.\u8221"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Placing the phone down, the woman leaned back, avoiding the pod parked behind her. \u8220"Hey Jones! We\u8217've got another one of those Project Restoration freaks! Send a team to deal with it!\u8221"\par}
